      		</div>
      		
			<div class="comment-text"><p>My choices are the pie and stacked bar chart &#8211; &#8220;best&#8221; would depend on what I wanted to emphasize. The stacked bar chart is better for relating categories against each other, while the pie chart does a better job of describing the relative importance of a single category to the whole. For example, from the stacked bar chart I clearly see that &#8220;statistical visualization&#8221; received the largest share of the votes by a wide margin. However, from the pie chart I see that it did not really dominate the voting.</p>
</div>

